" bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> こわす[C1]: to break (something) </td>    <td width="50%" bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> こわれる[C2]: to become broken </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td width="50%" bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> つける[C2]: to attach, to turn (something)      on </td>    <td width="50%" bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> つく[C1]: to stick, become attached</td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 消す[C1]: to put out, to extinguish, to turn off </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 消える[C2]: to go off, to disappear</td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 動かす[C1]:to move (something) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 動く[C1]: to move (by itself), to be in motion </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 止める[C2]: to stop (something) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 止まる[C1]: to come to a stop </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td width="50%" bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 落とす[C1]: to drop (something) </td>    <td width="50%" bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 落ちる[C2]: to fall (from a height)</td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> かける[C2]:to hang (something on), to take (time) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> かかる[C1]: to hang, to take (time)</td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 乗せる[C2]: to put on a vehicle, to give a ride to </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 乗る[C1]: to board a vehicle, to ride </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 回す[C1]: to turn (something), to send around </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 回る[C1]: to turn around, to go around </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> かえる[C2]: to change (something) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> かわる[C1]:to (undergo) change </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 始める[C2]: to begin (something) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"> 始まる[C1]: to begin </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td bgcolor="#D5E6FF"> 終わる[C1]／終える[C2]: to end (something) </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"><p>終わる&nbsp;[C1]: to (come to an ) end </p></td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td colspan="2" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">Additional pairs </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">集(あつ)める[C2]: to gather (things/people)</td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF"><p>集(あつ)まる&nbsp;[C1]: to congregate </p>      </td>    </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">見つける[C2]: to find </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">見つかる&nbsp;[C1]: to be found </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">残す&nbsp;[C1]: to leave behind </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">残る&nbsp;[C1]: to be left, to remain </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">並べる[C2]: to line (things) up </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">並ぶ&nbsp;[C1]: to get in line </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">寝かす&nbsp;[C1]: to put to bed </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">寝る[C2]: to go to bed, to sleep </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">切る&nbsp;[C1]: to cut</td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">切れる[C2]: to be cut </td>  </tr>  <tr>    <td height="36" bgcolor="#D5E6FF">着る[C2]: to wear </td>    <td bgcolor="#EFFCFF">着せる[C2]: to fit cloth on someone, to frame someone </td>  </tr></table><p>&nbsp;</p><ul>  <LI>Transitive and Intransitive verbs --pairs　<a href="gl_y2_ch3_transintransverbpairs.pdf">pdf      format</a></LI></UL>          <ul>        <li><B>練習 (Practice Quizzes)</B>        </li>        <ul>	      <li><a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412k/gq_y2_412k_tearuteiruteokuteiru.php">Transitive	          verb-ている、Transitive verb-てある、Intransitive verb-ている、〜ておく、〜ところ</a>)</li>	      <li><a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412k/gq_y2_412k_transintrans_pairs.php">Transitive and Intransitive	          verb pairs</a> (verbs) </li>	      <li><a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412k/gq_y2_412k_intranstrans_verbpart.php">Transitive and Intransitive	          verbs -- particles</a> </li>	      <li><a href="../../../gquiz/y2/412k/gq_y2_412k_yootosurutemiru.php">〜ようとする、〜てみる、and transitive/intransitive	          verbs</a> </li>        </ul>        </LI>		    <p align="center"><a href="#top">Return to Top</a> </p>		    <p align="center"><a href="../../../